"title": "3025: Holy Spirit, personality of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "3025",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The Holy Spirit is not an impersonal power but a real person with his own personality.</p>\n<h2>The Holy Spirit is involved in personal relationships</h2>\n<h3>He is in relationship with the Father and the Son</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt28:19\">MAT 28:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:14-John16:15\">JHN 16:14–16:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor13:14\">2CO 13:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:2\">1PE 1:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:20-Jude1:21\">JUD 1:20–1:21</a></p>\n<h3>He is in relationship with Christians</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:28\">ACT 15:28</a></strong></p>\n<h3>The Spirit can be treated in personal ways</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:3\">ACT 5:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:9\">ACT 5:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:29\">HEB 10:29</a></p>\n<h2>Personal characteristics of the Holy Spirit</h2>\n<h3>The Spirit is wise</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa11:2\">ISA 11:2</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:17\">EPH 1:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:26\">JHN 14:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:27\">ROM 8:27</a></p>\n<h3>The Spirit can experience emotion and pain</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:30\">EPH 4:30</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa63:10\">ISA 63:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:29\">HEB 10:29</a></p>\n<h2>Grammatical indications of the Holy Spirit's personhood</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:16\">JHN 14:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:26\">JHN 14:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:26\">JHN 15:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:7\">JHN 16:7</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of the Holy Spirit's actions</h2>\n<p>He teaches:\n <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:12\">LUK 12:12</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor2:13\">1CO 2:13</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:16\">ROM 8:16</a> <em>He testifies</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:26\">ROM 8:26</a> <em>He intercedes</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:23\">ACT 20:23</a> <em>He warns</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam23:2\">2SA 23:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:29\">ACT 8:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:19\">ACT 10:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts11:12\">ACT 11:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:2\">ACT 13:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:7\">REV 2:7</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor2:11\">1CO 2:11</a> <em>He knows</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal4:6\">GAL 4:6</a> <em>He calls out</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:13\">JHN 16:13</a> <em>He hears</em></p>\n<h2>The Holy Spirit's own personality is seen by the gifts he gives and the attitudes he promotes</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:22-Gal5:23\">GAL 5:22–5:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:21\">LUK 10:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:31\">ACT 9:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:5\">ROM 5:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:6\">ROM 8:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom14:17\">ROM 14:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:13\">ROM 15:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor13:14\">2CO 13:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John1:6\">1JN 1:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:6\">1JN 5:6</a></p>",
